t-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Viet Nam\" title=\"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/bxh-fifa-thang-42018-dt-viet-nam-tang-truong-manh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u0103ng 10 b\u1eadc tr\u00ean&nbsp;BXH FIFA th\u00e1ng 4/2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf \u0110N\u00c1 l\u00e0 \u0110T Philippines. Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh Azkals \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng 9 b\u1eadc so v\u1edbi th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng h\u1ea1ng 113 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 3.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u0169ng t\u0103ng 7 b\u1eadc l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng 122. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c c\u0169ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng. Myanmar t\u0103ng 7 b\u1eadc l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng 135, Malaysia t\u0103ng 8 b\u1eadc l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng 170. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Indonesia l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u0103ng b\u1eadc \u1edf h\u1ea1ng 162 TG.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c1, 6 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi Iran v\u1eabn d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u, ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn \u00dac, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Arab X\u00ea-\u00fat v\u00e0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ee5t h\u1ea1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Kyrgyzstan. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n 40 b\u1eadc so v\u1edbi th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng 75 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 6 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Trong th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Kyrgyzstan th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u01b0\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi 282 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u BXH FIFA th\u00e1ng 4/2018 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, x\u1ebfp sau l\u00e0 Brazil. \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng hai b\u1eadc l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng 3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 Argentina xu\u1ed1ng c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ebfp theo.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">BXH FIFA ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 17/5.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1095","checkdouble":"184106"},{"date":"16:36 12/04","title":"Sau hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng U23, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/12/sau-hieu-ung-u23-bong-da-viet-nam-co-them-nha-tai-tro-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size: