a Real Madrid vs Juventus.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-khien-ca-the-gioi-can-loi-khi-lap-sieu-pham-vao-luoi-juve-184-183489.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cris Ronaldo khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u00e1n ph\u1ee5c v\u1edbi si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ng\u1ea3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e8n</span> qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. T\u00ednh \u1edf kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;bay nh\u01b0 chim&rdquo; \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 cao h\u01a1n 2m, khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Buffon h\u00f3a g\u00e3 h\u1ec1 n\u01a1i khung g\u1ed7. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh CR7, v\u00e0 anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\"><br>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18\" title=\"T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 201718 K\u1ecbch t\u00ednh, b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 tranh c\u00e3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Tu-ket-Champions-League-201718-Kich-tinh,-bat-ngo-va-tranh-cai-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ng\u1ea3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e8n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ebfp theo, ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m &ldquo;h\u1ee5t&rdquo; mang t\u00ean Bernardo Silva trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Man City vs Liverpool. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 do c\u00f4ng Jesus, v\u00e0 \u00e9p s\u00e2n The Kop to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Bernardo Silva th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00fang c\u1ed9t, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 2-0 v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, Man xanh gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft ngay \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn v\u00ec vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb, tr\u00fang khung g\u1ed7 c\u00f9ng chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00fat ra (c\u1ee7a Mane), \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quay ngo\u1eaft 180 \u0111\u1ed9. Mohamed Salah trong m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng ghi b\u00e0n 1-1, khi\u1ebfn Man City \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 ghi th\u00eam 4 b\u00e0n. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, pha \u0103n m\u1eebng d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u00e0n ph\u00e1o xanh c\u1ee7a &ldquo;Vua Ai C\u1eadp&rdquo; th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Barca vs AS Roma, m\u1ecdi con m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o Manolas c\u00f9ng De Rossi. 2 t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc <strong>&ldquo;l\u1ee1 ch\u00e2n&rdquo; ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0</strong>, gi\u1edd h\u00f3a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng b\u1eb1ng 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3, t\u1ea1o ra <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/nhung-yeu-to-khien-barca-bi-roma-nguoc-dong-ngoan-muc-184-184057.html\" target=\"_blank\">c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18</span>. M\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u00f4i ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roma ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1ea7n th\u00e1nh t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18\" title=\"Manolas ghi ban quyet dinh cho Roma 3-0 Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/hinh-anh-roma-an-mung-trong-phong-thay-do-sau-ky-tich-thang-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ni\u1ec1m vui kh\u00f4n t\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a AS Roma sau khi Manolas ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 mang t\u00ean tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Juventus, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thi\u00ean v\u1ecb CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, &ldquo;vua th\u1ebb&rdquo; Cuneyt Cakir th\u1eb3ng tay tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t Paulo Dybala v\u00ec l\u1ed7i \u0103n v\u1ea1 v\u00e0 cao ch\u00e2n, khi\u1ebfn Juve s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en kh\u00e1c &ndash; Michael Oliver c\u1ee7a v\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u1ed1c Anh. Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, r\u00fat th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00ec l\u1ed7i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Buffon, qua \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c khi\u1ebfn Juve \u00f4m h\u1eadn. Sau tr\u1eadn, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/ong-ta-la-ke-giet-nguoi-mau-lanh-ke-khong-co-trai-tim-184-184070.html\" target=\"_blank\">Oliver b\u1ecb Buffon g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 k\u1ebb gi\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tr\u00e1i tim</span>.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Antonio Mateu Lahoz c\u0169ng tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola ngay sau hi\u1ec7p 1, khi\u1ebfn Man City g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 Liverpool. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League \u0111\u00e0nh ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Cup C1, khi thua to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juve 2 l\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18\" title=\"Buffon phan ung voi trong tai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/buffon-phan-ung-trong-tai-tran-real-vs-juventus-co-the-thong-cam-duoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juve 2 l\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu ch\u1ecdn ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a AS Roma. T\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u0129nh h\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stade Olimpico \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1, v\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u00e9p s\u00e2n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i. 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Dzeko, De Rossi v\u00e0 Manolas l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 qu\u00e1 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho B\u1ea7y s\u00f3i, khi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 cho r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-roma-vs-barca-01h45-ngay-114-champions-league-201718-372-183963.html\" target=\"_blank\">c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n lo\u1ea1i Barca</span>, chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Roma c\u00f2n cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd m\u1ea5t \u0111i \u1edf Cup C1. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c to l\u1edbn d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Juventus &ndash; CLB c\u0169ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi t\u00e2m th\u1ebf th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a Mandzukic t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Croatia l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf ph\u00fat 37, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Matuidi n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-0 ngay t\u1ea1i Bernabeu. Nh\u00ecn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u00f4m l\u1ea5y tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Bianconeri &ndash; khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n (d\u00f9 sau c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"2 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Italia ch\u01a1i ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18\" title=\"Matuidi nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c sau khi ghi b\u00e0n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/tinhthanjuve.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>2 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u1ec1u thi \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft trong m\u01a1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ee5m t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng cho Man City vs Barca &ndash; 2 CLB xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Cup C1, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u00e2u n\u00f3i l\u1ed1 b\u1ecbch, khi c\u1ea3 CLB hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u1eabn qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola \u0111\u1ec1u thua nh\u1ee5c nh\u00e3. Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft trong m\u01a1, <strong>gi\u1edd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh... trong m\u01a1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Liverpool, nh\u01b0ng Man xanh b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 ngay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh v\u1edbi \u0111\u00eam \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i Anfield. H\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thua s\u1ed1c trong tr\u1eadn derby th\u00e0nh Manchester \u00edt ng\u00e0y sau \u0111\u00f3, r\u1ed3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i 1 tu\u1ea7n &ldquo;ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o&rdquo; c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc The Kop, l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ngay \u1edf Etihad, khi Pep c\u00f2n b\u1ecb tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"&quot;Th\u00e1nh Salah&quot; h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Man City \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18\" title=\"Th\u00e1nh Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/salah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&quot;Th\u00e1nh Salah&quot; h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Man City \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/barca-bi-roma-loai-khoi-champions-league-khong-dep-khong-co-quyen-184-184089.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m</span>, khi t\u1ef1 tay v\u1ee9t b\u1ecf l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. B\u1eb9p d\u00ed t\u1ea1i Olimpico khi nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c, r\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1ng cu\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0a bom t\u1ea5n 150 tri\u1ec7u euro Dembele v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, Barca \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed&rdquo; theo c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch ch\u1eb3ng ai mong \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, 4 CLB cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Real Madrid, Bayern Munich, Liverpool v\u00e0 AS Roma. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia c\u1eb7p s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i mai (13/4).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ket qua tu ket Champions League 2017/18\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/tu-ket-champions-league-kich-tinh-bat-ngo-va-tran-chung-ket-trong-mo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Cup C1<br>\r\n</strong> <br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/marcelo-dung-mo-chung-toi-bi-loai-nhu-barca-184-184075.html\">Marcelo: &ldquo;\u0110\u1eebng m\u01a1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Barca&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-bao-gio-messi-thanh-liet-si-cua-barca-180-183894.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Bao gi\u1edd Messi th\u00e0nh &ldquo;li\u1ec7t s\u0129&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Barca?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hau-tu-ket-champions-league-201718-khi-ranh-gioi-ong-lon-da-nhat-nhoa-184-184102.html\">H\u1eadu t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18: Khi ranh gi\u1edbi \u00f4ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/quan-diem-barca-phai-cam-on-nguoi-ban-tot-roma-184-183997.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: Barca ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t Roma</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-nhan-luot-di-tu-ket-champions-league-2-ga-hoi-dau-va-4-chiec-ve-co-chu-184-183588.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League: 2 g\u00e3 h\u00f3i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 4 chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 c\u00f3 ch\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-30-man-city-xin-chao-day-la-anfield-184-183570.html\">Liverpool 3-0 Man City: Xin ch\u00e0o, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Anfield!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1089","checkdouble":"184111"},{"date":"15:31 12/04","title":"Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a Mourinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/juventus-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-tro-cung-cua-mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate2>a:hover{color:#f00;text-de