g nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1987 \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kha nang Marouane Fellaini toi Juventus khong the xay ra  hinh anh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Marouane Fellaini t\u1edbi Juventus kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Kha-nang-Marouane-Fellaini-toi-Juventus-khong-the-xay-ra--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marouane Fellaini t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Fellaini \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ngo\u00e0i tai nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi th\u1ec9nh c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Mourinho. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Th\u1ef1c ra anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng M.U l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-thua-nhan-bat-luc-trong-viec-giu-chan-fellaini-172-180992.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Fellaini s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U</strong></span> trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Hi\u1ec7n anh \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap/bi-real-da-vang-khoi-champions-league-psg-tuc-toc-mua-sao-mu-197-181511.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>PSG quan t\u00e2m Fellaini</strong></span>, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i. Fellaini s\u1ebd r\u1eddi M.U theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 \u0111o, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd&nbsp;do t\u1ea1i sao anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Fellaini</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Marouane Fellaini t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU vs Sevilla Fellaini da chinh\" title=\"MU vs Sevilla Fellaini da chinh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/14/MU-that-bai-truoc-Sevilla-Show-dien-do-te-cua-Mou-United-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Marouane&nbsp; Fellaini t\u1edbi Juventus \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, song Juventus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Fellaini kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, b\u1edfi v\u1eady \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus nh\u01b0ng Fellaini c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1edfi anh \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. PSG c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Felalini \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. C\u00f3 tin cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u sao Everton. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Fellaini \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/21764-40942/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Fellaini \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1088","checkdouble":"184101"},{"date":"16:04 12/04","title":"Everton t\u1ef1 tin chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/16/everton-tu-tin-chieu-mo-sao-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate2>a:hover{color:#f00;te