0e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Everton mua Jack Wilshere o ky chuyen nhuong He 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"Everton mua Jack Wilshere \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/Everton-mua-Jack-Wilshere-o-ky-chuyen-nhuong-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jack Wilshere s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Arsenal ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Wilshere. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Wenger mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i, song \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/wilshere-noi-loi-cay-dang-voi-arsenal-172-181714.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Wilshere chia tay Arsenal</strong></span> \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Italia v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Everton quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Wilshere</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton mua Jack Wilshere nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Wilshere\" title=\"Jack Wilshere\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/1/wenger-du-sao-arsenal-o-lai-bang-chieu-doc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton mua Jack Wilshere n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo Football London, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf k\u1ef3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/chuyen-nhuong-c187-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</strong></span> H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Everton mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Walcott, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd \u0111ang t\u1ef1 tin trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00eda Everton s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Wilshere ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Everton mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Wilshere \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Wilshere mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Everton l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Wilshere \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/38094-40942/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Wilshere \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1087","checkdouble":"184103"},{"date":"16:36 12/04","title":"2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Barca",