 bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andre Gomes kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Barca, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/andre-gomes-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-180-183818.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Gomes c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</strong></span>, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i hay \u1edf v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham va West Ham muon dua Andre Gomes roi Barca  hinh anh\" title=\"Tottenham v\u00e0 West Ham mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Andre Gomes r\u1eddi Barca  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/14/2-doi-bong-thanh-london-dai-chien-vi-sao-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Andre Gomes r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gomes r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ng\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 25 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-chi-195-trieu-bang-cuop-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-man-city-172-130268.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>M.U \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Gomes</strong></span>, Juventus v\u00e0 PSG c\u0169ng gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ef1u sao Valencia \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham v\u00e0 West Ham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Gomes</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham v\u00e0 West Ham \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a Andre Gomes r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 25 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Andre Gomes\" title=\"tien ve Andre Gomes\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/16/MU-va-Man-City-vao-cuoc,-Andre-Gomes-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tottenham v\u00e0 West Ham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Andre Gomes</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea3 Tottenham v\u00e0 West Ham \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTottenham \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n West Ham, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn West Ham kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gomes \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 cao h\u01a1n. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 n\u1ebfu c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u01b0a bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Andre Gomes \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/235460-42556/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Andre Gomes \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1086","checkdouble":"184107"},{"date":"17:07 12/04","title":"Drinkwate