gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u song anh ch\u01b0a ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Drinkwater roi Chelsea chi sau mot mua giai hinh anh\" title=\"Danny Drinkwater r\u1eddi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/5/Danny-Drinkwater-roi-Chelsea-chi-sau-mot-mua-giai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danny Drinkwater kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nT\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge, Drinkwater kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 4 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, sau Kante, Fabregas v\u00e0 Bakayoko. T\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a anh m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh 5 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Premier League.</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nHLV Conte kh\u00f4ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nCh\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb d\u00e0i d\u00e0i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i. Anh c\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh.</div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Drinkwater s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Chelsea n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div>Theo The Guardian, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/danny-drinkwater-52577.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Danny Drinkwater</strong></span> r\u1eddi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea 0-0 Arsenal Maitland-Niles va Drinkwater\" title=\"Chelsea 0-0 Arsenal Maitland-Niles va Drinkwater\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/11/tong-hop-chelsea-00-arsenal-ban-ket-league-cup-201718.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Drinkwater c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Juventus v\u00e0 PSG, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Drinkwater r\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nV\u1edbi<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/chelsea-6.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> Chelsea</strong></span>, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. 32 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c The Blues nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Kante \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n Chelsea trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf Leicester, anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Drinkwater ra \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Drinkwater \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/54330-40942/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Drinkwater \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1085","checkdouble":"184108"},{"date":"16:46 12/04","title":"Nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t cho gameweek 34 FPL","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/12/nhung-lua-chon-sang-gia-gameweek-34-fantasy-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;p