-right,.ui-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>David De Gea (M.U)</strong><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ecdi ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh, David De Gea (gi\u00e1 5.9) lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1. G\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 West Brom (S\u00e2n nh\u00e0) r\u1ed3i Bournemouth (S\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch), c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh trung b\u00ecnh 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1edf l\u00ean c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng cao. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nGameweek 34 Fantasy Premier League quy \u0111\u1ecbnh 2 tr\u1eadn ch\u1eadp l\u1ea1i l\u00e0m 1 v\u00e0 theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 De Gea gi\u00e0nh 12 \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec3m Bonus v\u00e0 c\u1ee9u thua. Hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 25 ngh\u00ecn l\u01b0\u1ee3t mua s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Man United v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung lua chon sang gia Gameweek 34 Fantasy Premier League  hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 Gameweek 34 Fantasy Premier League  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Nhung-lua-chon-sang-gia-Gameweek-34-Fantasy-Premier-League--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>De Gea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu \u1edf Gameweek 34 Fantasy Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Kasper Schmeichel (Leicester)</strong><br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Man United, Leicester c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngon ngh\u1ebb \u1edf Gameweek 34 Fantasy Premier League. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, B\u1ea7y c\u00e1o ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng Burnley (SK) v\u00e0 Southampton (SN) v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e0i n\u0103ng b\u1eaft penalty \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng (c\u1ea3n qu\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 qu\u1ea3 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf n\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Schmeichel. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 5.1 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i ng\u1ea1i ng\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Marcos Alonso (Chelsea)</strong><br>\r\nM\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 7.2 c\u1ee7a Alonso hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 cao nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 trong game. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 n\u00e0o ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n s\u1ed1 3 c\u1ee7a Chelsea (12) ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Chelsea v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Alonso ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf. Nh\u1eefng Southampton hay Burnley \u0111\u1ec1u thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng k\u00e9m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng ai s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 kha kh\u00e1 \u1edf Gameweek 34 Fantasy Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung lua chon sang gia nhat cho gameweek 34 FPL hinh anh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t cho gameweek 34 FPL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Nhung-lua-chon-sang-gia-nhat-cho-gameweek-34-FPL-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Marcos Alonso c\u1ee7a Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Chris Smalling (M.U)</strong><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cho M.U v\u00e0 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc De Gea l\u00e0 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Smalling. Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng \u1edf m\u1ee9c 5.5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 West Brom (SN) r\u1ed3i Bournemouth (SK) c\u00e0ng th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y l\u01b0\u1ee3ng mua Smalling t\u0103ng cao. Hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 60 ngh\u00ecn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u201ctransfers in\u201d s\u1ed1 12 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Gameweek 34. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7n nhanh tay b\u1edfi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Smalling b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00ean 5.6 trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi l\u00e0 h\u01a1n 90%.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>James Tarkowski (Burnley)</strong><br>\r\nBurnley trong 2 n\u0103m qua lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. Ri\u00eang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y, nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f2n gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n n\u1eefa b\u1edfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n Gameweek 34 (Leicester, Chelsea) v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Gameweek 35 (Stoke).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ben Mee ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Tarkowski ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Burnley. Anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 trung t\u00e2m trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung lua chon sang gia nhat cho gameweek 34 FPL hinh anh 3\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t cho gameweek 34 FPL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Nhung-lua-chon-sang-gia-nhat-cho-gameweek-34-FPL-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">James Tarkowski c\u1ee7a Burnley</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Harry Maguire (Leicester) </strong><br>\r\nC\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Schmeichel, Harry Maguire n\u1eb1m trong h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Leicester \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Burnley (SK) v\u00e0 Southampton (SN) t\u1ea1i Gameweek 34 Fantasy Premier League. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 15 B\u1ea7y s\u00f3i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCon s\u1ed1 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o m\u00f9a n\u00e0y l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Kh\u00fac m\u1eafc duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Maguire ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 5.6 \u1edf m\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5p so v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng c\u1ee7a Leicester.</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Alexis Sanchez (M.U)</strong><br>\r\nL\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 14 v\u00e0 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau 2 gameweek v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. Ngay c\u1ea3 Man City, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile c\u0169ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00ec nh\u1eefng West Brom (SN) r\u1ed3i Bournemouth (SK) c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u201cm\u1ed3i ngon\u201d c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac Sanchez b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi M.U v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n cao \u0111\u1ed9. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alexis Sanchez tai MU\" title=\"Alexis Sanchez tai MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Alexis-Sanchez-tai-MU.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Alexis Sanchez \u0111ang h\u1ed3i sinh t\u1ea1i M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Willian (Chelsea)</strong><br>\r\nTh\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Chelsea th\u1eddi gian qua kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t song h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1ed1p 4 t\u1ea1i Premier League. M\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Southampton (SK) v\u00e0 Burnley (SK) l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 The Blues t\u00edch l\u0169y \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 s\u01a1 s\u1ea9y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Chelsea, Willian l\u00e0 s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 7.2 c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Eden Hazard (10.6) trong khi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 trong th\u1eddi gian qua. S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t mua Willian v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t con s\u1ed1 h\u01a1n 38 ngh\u00ecn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Riyad Mahrez (Leicester)</strong><br>\r\nNh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Leicester kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n g\u00ec trong 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton v\u00e0 Newcastle. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i Fantasy \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c khi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft anh l\u00e0 Burnley (SK) v\u00e0 Southampton (SN).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Leicester, Mahrez v\u1eabn l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 20 ngh\u00ecn l\u01b0\u1ee3t mua t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 10 b\u00e0n, 11 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 30 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Gameweek 34 Fantasy Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Riyad Mahrez\" title=\"tien ve Riyad Mahrez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/tien-ve-Riyad-Mahrez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u00e3 t\u1edbi l\u00fac Riyad Mahrez b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Romelu Lukaku (M.U)</strong><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Nh\u01b0ng v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh trong game Fantasy kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb n\u00e2ng l\u00ean. V\u1eabn c\u00f2n k\u1ecbp cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i nhanh tay mang Lukaku v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean 11.6.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng West Brom (SN) v\u00e0 Bournemouth (SK) l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Lukaku ch\u1ee9ng minh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn trong s\u1ed1 29,6% s\u1ed1 HLV trong game \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u00e2n 3 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Lukaku v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y (Triple Captain). T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1ed1 9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Romelu Lukaku\" title=\"tien dao Romelu Lukaku\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/tien-dao-Romelu-Lukaku.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Harry Kane (Tottenham)</strong><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Stoke gi\u00fap Harry Kane (25) ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah (29) c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn cho tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh trong cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi Man City (SN) v\u00e0 Brighton (SK) l\u00e0 2 trong s\u1ed1 6 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 Kane l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Salah v\u00e0 Liverpool ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 5 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 10 Tottenham. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, Kane thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o h\u00e0ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c HLV trong Gameweek 34 Fantasy Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Jamie Vardy (Leicester)</strong><br>\r\nTrong danh s\u00e1ch c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Gameweek 34 Fantasy Premier League, Vardy \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 (h\u01a1n 64 ngh\u00ecn l\u01b0\u1ee3t), ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m Kane (h\u01a1n 93 ngh\u00ecn l\u01b0\u1ee3t) v\u00e0 tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 Lukaku (h\u01a1n 61 ngh\u00ecn l\u01b0\u1ee3t).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n3 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua, Vardy \u0111\u1ec1u ghi b\u00e0n cho Leicester. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Burnley (SK) v\u00e0 Southampton (SN), d\u0129 nhi\u00ean anh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Fantasy Premier League tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/fantasy-epl/dang-ky-fantasy-premier-league-201718-tren-bongda24h-172-165545.html\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n trong Fantasy Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/fantasy-epl/cach-choi-fantasy-premier-league-201718-tren-bongda24h-172-165549.html\">Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Fantasy Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/fantasy-epl/gioi-thieu-fantasy-premier-league-mua-201718-bongda24h-172-165568.html\">Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u t\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 game Fantasy Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/fantasy-epl/cach-choi-fantasy-premier-league-mua-201718-bongda24h-172-165581.html\">C\u00e1ch qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong Fantasy Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/fantasy-epl/nhung-cau-hoi-thuong-gap-trong-fantasy-premier-league-433-165654.html\">Nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p khi ch\u01a1i Fantasy Premier League</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThi\u00ean Th\u1ed5 (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1084","checkdouble":"184110"},{"date":"10:26 12/04","title":"HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt gi\u00fap \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/13/hlv-mai-duc-chung-tiet-lo-chien-thuat-giup-dt-nu-viet-nam-tao-bat-ngo-truoc-han-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px