0e1i ng\u00e0y 8/3 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Trong ng\u00e0y Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea5ng m\u00e0y r\u00e2u t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 du l\u1ecbch n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u1eb3n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn khi r\u1ee7 v\u1ee3, b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Camp Nou.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ecb em v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u00ean &ldquo;th\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ecba&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Barca h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1ea7n th\u00e1nh. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Paris Saint-Germain d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 4-0 sau tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra khi h\u1ecd th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 6-1 khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eadt l\u1ea1i t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca bi Roma loai khoi Champions League voi bo mat xau xi hinh anh\" title=\"Barca b\u1ecb Roma lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t x\u1ea5u x\u00ed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/25/Barca-bi-Roma-loai-khoi-Champions-League-voi-bo-mat-xau-xi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc PSG</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 l\u00e0m chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed3n nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c Cules hay ch\u1ecb em xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. \u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thua 4 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng knock-out Champions League r\u1ed3i v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Tuy nhi\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/du-am-tran-dau-barca-61-psg-vong-18-champions-league-184-155534.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1edfi nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c</strong></span>, c\u1ea3 v\u00f4 h\u00ecnh l\u1eabn h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 3, 10/4 v\u1eeba qua, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta tin r\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 quy lu\u1eadt vay tr\u1ea3. Barca \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 y h\u1ebft bi k\u1ecbch m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gieo cho PSG c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n 1 n\u0103m. D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 4-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, trung v\u1ec7 Gerard Pique c\u00f2n ao \u01b0\u1edbc g\u1eb7p Real Madrid \u1edf v\u00f2ng sau. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1&hellip;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i m\u00e3n cu\u1ed9c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Olimpico vang l\u00ean, Roma \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Barca 3-0. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia gi\u1eadt t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng n\u1eb1m ch\u1eafc trong tay \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Barca tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t h\u1ed1c h\u00e1c, hoang mang nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tin vi\u1ec7c m\u00ecnh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barcelona bi loai nhuc nha\" title=\"Barcelona bi loai nhuc nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/HLV-Valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-Roma-vs-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>H\u01a1n 1 n\u0103m sau, Barca b\u1ecb Roma lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League trong cay \u0111\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Roma \u0111\u1eb9p, Barca x\u1ea5u x\u00ed</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i m\u1eb7t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Barcelona v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua PSG h\u01a1n 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i. H\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n m\u00e0 pha quay ch\u1eadm cho th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. Trong su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua, Blaugrana c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng \u01b0u \u00e1i t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb &ldquo;Vua \u00e1o \u0111en&rdquo; n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 UEFA n\u00f3i chung.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u1edfi Barca \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep Guardiola hay Luis Enrique c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn. UEFA hay m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecd d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i Champions League xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u n\u1eb7ng v\u1ec1 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n v\u00e0 h\u01a1i t\u1ebb nhat.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca bat luc truoc lao tuong nhu Dzeko\" title=\"Barca bat luc truoc lao tuong nh\u01b0 Dzeko\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-as-roma-30-barcelona.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t x\u1ea5u x\u00ed</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu x\u00e9t tr\u00ean ti\u00eau ch\u00ed n\u00e0y, Barca c\u1ee7a Valverde kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c UEFA lo toan. V\u00ec y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n m\u1edbi t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2017/18 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng che m\u1edd \u0111i c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a CLB. Ch\u1ea5t Tiki-Taka \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Johan Cruyff truy\u1ec1n th\u1ee5 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng b\u1edfi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eddi HLV Barca nay tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ea5t m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u trong vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1edbi Barca, Valverde ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn n\u00e0o. \u00d4ng quanh qu\u1ea9n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Espanyol, Villarreal hay Athletic Bilbao&hellip; v\u00e0 t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng &ldquo;h\u00f2a l\u00e0 may&rdquo; trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde\" title=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-roma-vs-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Blaugrana \u0111ang l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i d\u01b0\u1edbi tay Valverde</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League v\u1edbi Roma, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/phan-doi-loi-choi-barca-thoi-valverde-la-trach-nhiem-cua-cules-180-182988.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Valverde \u0111\u00e3 mang tri\u1ebft l\u00fd ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean Barca</strong></span>. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd d\u00f9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Italia, t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p l\u1ea1i d\u00e2ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n qua l\u1ea1i. Thay v\u00ec t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n, g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 d\u01b0\u1edbi tay Valverde l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 h\u1ec5 c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 giao ngay cho si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-roma-vs-barca-184-183984.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-roma-vs-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-roma-vs-barca-184-183984.html\">HLV Barca n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau \u0111\u00eam kinh ho\u00e0ng t\u1ea1i Olimpico?</span><br>\r\n<span>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Olimpico \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Barcelona. HLV Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Roma vs Barca c\u0169ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng may, Messi b\u1ecb t\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u trong \u0111\u00eam Olimpico c\u00f2n Barca th\u00ec l\u1ee5i b\u1ea1i. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Valverde ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t l\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 v\u1ed1n li\u1ebfng 3 b\u00e0n c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i? OK. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1 r\u1ed3i 2 b\u00e0n, Barca v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00e1o xanh xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f4ng h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi co the mat bong vang la he qua sau tran thua cua Barca\" title=\"Messi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/mesi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Messi kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nhi\u1ec1u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u1ecdi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng sai. Barca n\u00e0o c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ch\u0103m ch\u0103m chuy\u1ec1n qua chuy\u1ec1n l\u1ea1i cho th\u1eddi gian mau k\u1ebft th\u00fac. V\u00e0 c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 cho m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 t\u1ef1 thu nh\u1ecf m\u00ecnh l\u1ea1i, m\u1ed9t ch\u00fa thi\u00ean nga t\u1ef1 b\u00f4i x\u1ea5u m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t bi k\u1ecbch \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/quan-diem-barca-phai-cam-on-nguoi-ban-tot-roma-184-183997.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Roma 3-0 Barca</strong></span> v\u00e0 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft sau g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n t\u1ea1m n\u1eb1m trong tay th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Valverde \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ee7. Ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 n\u00e9m \u0111i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n 1 n\u0103m, khi b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua PSG nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 thi\u00ean v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Barca v\u1ed7 ng\u1ef1c: T\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb9p, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n. N\u1ebfu suy ngh\u0129 theo h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u00f3, Barca b\u1ecb Roma lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League c\u0169ng l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. M\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i t\u1ef1 b\u00f4i x\u1ea5u m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Barcelona tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/quan-diem-barca-phai-cam-on-nguoi-ban-tot-roma-184-183997.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: Barca ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n t\u1ed1t Roma</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thay-gi-sau-man-nguoc-dong-khong-tuong-cua-roma-truoc-barca-184-183976.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Roma tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-bao-gio-messi-thanh-liet-si-cua-barca-180-183894.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Bao gi\u1edd Messi th\u00e0nh &ldquo;li\u1ec7t s\u0129&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Barca?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sevilla-vs-barcelona-nhiet-liet-hoan-ho-valvelona-180-183298.html\">Barca h\u00f2a v\u1ebb vang Sevilla: Nhi\u1ec7t li\u1ec7t hoan h\u00f4 &ldquo;Valvelona&rdquo;!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/phan-doi-loi-choi-barca-thoi-valverde-la-trach-nhiem-cua-cules-180-182988.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: Ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i &ldquo;Valvelona&rdquo; l\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c cules</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-loi-choi-real-va-barca-180-182545.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: \u0110\u00e2y Real v\u00e0 Bernabeu, kia Barca v\u00e0 Camp Nou&hellip;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1078","checkdouble":"184089"}]}